║                              ZOOM PRO                                     ║
╚═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╝

ZOOM PRO — is the premium version of the world's leading video communication platform, offering unlimited meeting duration, advanced administrative features, cloud recording, and enhanced collaboration tools. This professional-grade solution transforms how teams connect, collaborate, and communicate across distances. With support for up to 1,000 interactive participants and 10,000 view-only attendees, Zoom Pro is ideal for businesses, educational institutions, and enterprises of all sizes.

