    ⚡ HOW THE PROGRAM WORKS:
    ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
    
    🔹 CORE TECHNOLOGY
    Zoom Pro utilizes a cloud-based architecture that combines high-quality video conferencing with enterprise-grade security. The platform leverages distributed data centers worldwide to ensure low latency and high availability. The client application runs on your local machine while connecting to Zoom's global network, which handles video routing, recording storage, and meeting management .
    
    🔹 MEETING CAPABILITIES
    
    • UNLIMITED MEETING DURATION: No 40-minute time limit on group meetings
    • UP TO 1,000 PARTICIPANTS: Standard Pro license supports 100 participants (add-on available for 500-1,000)
    • 10,000 VIEW-ONLY ATTENDEES: Large-scale events with view-only participants
    • HD VIDEO AND AUDIO: 1080p video quality with high-fidelity audio
    • SCREEN SHARING: Full desktop, specific applications, or virtual whiteboard
    • DUAL MONITOR SUPPORT: Separate screens for gallery view and shared content
    • TOUCH-UP APPEARANCE: Soft-focus filter for video enhancement
    • VIRTUAL BACKGROUNDS: Custom backgrounds without green screen
    • STUDIO EFFECTS: Filters, frames, and video avatars
    • NOISE CANCELLATION: AI-powered background noise suppression
    
    🔹 MEETING MANAGEMENT
    
    • SCHEDULING INTEGRATION: Calendar integration with Google, Outlook, iCal
    • RECURRING MEETINGS: Set up daily, weekly, or custom recurring meetings
    • MEETING TEMPLATES: Save and reuse meeting configurations
    • WAITING ROOM: Control participant entry with customizable lobby
    • REGISTRATION: Require registration for meetings and webinars
    • PASSCODE PROTECTION: Enhanced security with meeting passwords
    • LOCK MEETING: Prevent new participants from joining after start
    • MUTE ON ENTRY: Automatically mute participants when they join
    • DISABLE VIDEO: Control whether participants can start with video
    • BREAKOUT ROOMS: Split meeting into up to 100 separate sessions
    
    🔹 CLOUD RECORDING
    Zoom Pro includes 1GB of cloud recording storage per license:
    
    • AUTOMATIC RECORDING: Record meetings directly to the cloud
    • AUDIO TRANSCRIPTION: Automatic generation of meeting transcripts
    • RECORDING MANAGEMENT: Organize, share, and delete recordings
    • STREAMING LINKS: Generate shareable links for recorded meetings
    • DOWNLOAD OPTIONS: Download recordings in MP4 or M4A format
    • SMART CHAPTERS: AI-generated meeting chapters for easy navigation
    • RECORDING RETENTION: Customizable retention policies
    • PASSWORD PROTECTION: Secure shared recordings with passwords
    
    🔹 ADMINISTRATIVE FEATURES
    
    • USER MANAGEMENT: Add, remove, and manage users from web dashboard
    • GROUP SETTINGS: Apply settings to groups of users
    • ROLE-BASED ACCESS: Define roles with specific permissions
    • REPORTING: Usage reports, meeting history, registration reports
    • DASHBOARD: Real-time monitoring of ongoing meetings
    • BRANDING: Customize meeting interface with company logo and colors
    • SINGLE SIGN-ON: SAML, Google, Facebook, or SSO integration
    • DOMAIN MANAGEMENT: Control which email domains can join meetings
    • AUDIT LOGS: Track administrative actions for compliance
    
    🔹 WEBINAR FEATURES (Add-on)
    
    • INTERACTIVE Q&A: Panelists can answer attendee questions
    • POLLING: Create and launch polls during webinars
    • RAISE HAND: Attendees can indicate they have questions
    • ATTENDEE REPORTING: Detailed attendee engagement reports
    • PRACTICE SESSION: Rehearse before going live
    • PANELIST SUPPORT: Multiple panelists with video and audio
    • BRANDED REGISTRATION: Custom registration pages
    • SOCIAL MEDIA PROMOTION: Promote webinars on social platforms
    
    🔹 COLLABORATION TOOLS
    
    • IN-MEETING CHAT: Group and private messaging during meetings
    • FILE TRANSFER: Share files directly through chat
    • WHITEBOARD: Collaborative digital whiteboard with annotations
    • ANNOTATIONS: Draw and highlight on shared screens
    • REMOTE CONTROL: Request control of another participant's screen
    • NON-VERBAL FEEDBACK: Yes/no, go slower/faster indicators
    • EMOJI REACTIONS: Express reactions with emojis
    • BREAKOUT ROOMS: Small group discussions within larger meetings
    
    🔹 ZOOM CHAT (TEAM CHAT)
    
    • PERSISTENT CHAT: Team conversations that continue after meetings
    • CHANNELS: Public and private channels for team collaboration
    • DIRECT MESSAGES: One-on-one conversations with team members
    • FILE SHARING: Share files with team members
    • THREADED REPLIES: Organized conversations within channels
    • MENTIONS: @mention team members to get their attention
    • SYNTAX HIGHLIGHTING: Code snippets with language formatting
    • SEARCH: Search through chat history
    
    🔹 ZOOM PHONE (Add-on)
    
    • CLOUD PHONE SYSTEM: Enterprise phone system with Zoom
    • COMPANY DIRECTORY: Internal directory of company extensions
    • CALL RECORDING: Record incoming and outgoing calls
    • VOICEMAIL: Visual voicemail with transcription
    • CALL QUEUES: Automated call distribution
    • AUTO ATTENDANT: Professional call greeting and routing
    • SMS SUPPORT: Send and receive business text messages
    • INTERNATIONAL CALLING: Competitive rates for international calls
    
    🔹 ZOOM ROOMS (Add-on)
    
    • CONFERENCE ROOM INTEGRATION: Turn meeting rooms into Zoom Rooms
    • CALENDAR INTEGRATION: One-touch join from room calendar
    • WIRELESS SCREEN SHARING: Share content without cables
    • WHITEBOARD: Digital whiteboard in meeting rooms
    • ROOM SCHEDULING: Check availability and schedule rooms
    • MULTIPLE DISPLAYS: Support for up to 3 displays per room
    • AUDIO CONFERENCE: Integration with room audio systems
    
    🔹 SECURITY FEATURES
    
    • END-TO-END ENCRYPTION: E2EE for meetings (optional)
    • AES-256 ENCRYPTION: Standard encryption for all meetings
    • WAITING ROOM: Vetting participants before entry
    • AUTHENTICATION: Require authentication to join
    • SUSPICIOUS ACTIVITY DETECTION: AI monitoring for threats
    • DATA PRIVACY: Compliance with GDPR, HIPAA, and other regulations
    • ATTENDEE ANONYMITY: Anonymous join option for external participants
    • REPORTING: Detailed security and compliance reports
    
    🔹 INTEGRATIONS
    
    • MICROSOFT 365: Outlook, Teams, SharePoint integration
    • GOOGLE WORKSPACE: Gmail, Calendar, Drive integration
    • SLACK: Start meetings directly from Slack
    • SALESFORCE: Zoom meetings within Salesforce
    • HUBSPOT: Meeting integration with CRM
    • ZAPIER: Connect with 2,000+ apps
    • API ACCESS: Custom integrations with Zoom API
    • LMS INTEGRATION: Connect with Canvas, Blackboard, Moodle
    
    🔹 MOBILE EXPERIENCE
    
    • FULL FEATURED APPS: iOS and Android apps with all core features
    • JOIN ON THE GO: Join meetings from anywhere
    • MOBILE SCHEDULING: Schedule and start meetings from mobile
    • VIRTUAL BACKGROUNDS: Mobile support for background replacement
    • AIRPLAY/CHROMECAST: Cast meetings to TV
    • CARPLAY: Audio-only meetings in your car
    • WATCH APP: Apple Watch companion for quick actions
    
    🔹 ACCESSIBILITY FEATURES
    
    • LIVE TRANSCRIPTION: Real-time closed captions
    • KEYBOARD SHORTCUTS: Full keyboard navigation
    • SCREEN READER SUPPORT: Compatibility with JAWS, NVDA, VoiceOver
    • HIGH CONTRAST MODE: Enhanced visibility for visually impaired
    • FOCUS MODE: Presenter-only view for participants
    
    🔹 PERFORMANCE OPTIMIZATIONS
    
    • ADAPTIVE VIDEO: Adjusts quality based on network conditions
    • BANDWIDTH MANAGEMENT: Optimize for low-bandwidth environments
    • GPU ACCELERATION: Hardware acceleration for video processing
    • BACKGROUND BLUR: Low-resource alternative to virtual backgrounds
    • AUDIO-ONLY MODE: Switch to audio when video is unnecessary
    
    🔹 ANALYTICS AND REPORTING
    
    • USAGE DASHBOARD: Monitor meeting and webinar usage
    • PARTICIPANT REPORTS: Detailed attendance tracking
    • QUALITY REPORTS: Meeting quality and performance metrics
    • REGISTRATION REPORTS: Track webinar registrations
    • EXPORT CAPABILITIES: Export reports to CSV/PDF
    
    🔹 KEYBOARD SHORTCUTS
    
    ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
    Alt+A              │ Mute/unmute audio
    Alt+V              │ Start/stop video
    Alt+S              │ Start screen sharing
    Alt+R              │ Start/stop local recording
    Alt+C              │ Start/stop cloud recording
    Alt+P              │ Pause/resume recording
    Alt+N              │ Switch camera
    Alt+F              │ Enter/exit full screen
    Alt+Shift+S        │ Take screenshot
    ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
    
    🔹 PRO LICENSING FEATURES
    
    • SINGLE PRO LICENSE: Individual professional user license
    • BUSINESS LICENSE: Multiple users with admin management
    • ENTERPRISE LICENSE: Large organizations with advanced features
    • ADD-ONS: Webinar, Zoom Rooms, Zoom Phone (additional cost)
    • STORAGE UPGRADES: Additional cloud recording storage available
    ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

    ⚡ SYSTEM REQUIREMENTS:
    ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
    OS              │ Windows 7/8/10/11, macOS 10.9+, Linux (Ubuntu/Fedora/etc.)
    RAM             │ 4GB minimum (8GB+ recommended for HD video)
    CPU             │ Dual-core 2GHz or higher (quad-core for 1080p)
    GPU             │ DirectX 10 or OpenGL 2.0 compatible
    INTERNET        │ 1.5 Mbps up/down (minimum), 3.0 Mbps (recommended for HD)
    STORAGE         │ 200MB for installation + space for recordings
    DISPLAY         │ 1024×768 or higher resolution
    BROWSER         │ Chrome, Firefox, Edge, Safari for web client
    PERIPHERALS     │ Webcam, microphone, speakers (built-in or external)
